                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Sekond, your comment about indefinately adding content strikes true to me. Sony's idea of challenge is to make mobs insanely difficult to kill, and add gear that allows you to live through insane damage. Which breaks old content.
<br />

<br />
I'm pretty sure there are ways to keep adding content without totally breaking old content, but it requires some orginality of thought to add challenge without totally trivializing current content. Which I'm coming to believe that Sony is completely lacking in.
<br />

<br />
Myself, I'm patiently awaiting the coming of WoW and to see how that is, but my time in EQ is, I think, coming to a close.</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />Max
<br />
<a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=368646" target="_blank" class="postlink">Fanamax the Enchanter</a></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
